            <title>[SOLR-1141] Fix NPE during creating snapshot and clean up code</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1141</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If there is no new document added since the last snapshot is created, the request solr/replication?command=snapshoot &lt;br/&gt;
